{"tid":1380584,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「港獨」民陣同泛民快做嘢啦","createTime":"2019-07-29T05:06:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T02:21:19.000Z","uid":281918,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9e1a77b8eb1112376c57694289577bf61303a0d4","tid":1380584,"uid":281918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:06:00.000Z","msg":"民陣都俾人話港獨啦 快啲做嘢<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">宣布全港8月5日全港大罷工</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">仲有啲泛民議員 你哋有一定影響力<br />\n快啲開記者會宣傳罷工 有訪問就講 loop 到八月五<br />\n</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">罷工唔係facebook whatsapp 傳下就得<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">你哋有咁嘅airtime 就要好好珍惜</span></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n係電視講一句會多好多人知！</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n明報：【逃犯條例】人民日報海外版：民陣「港獨」屬性暴露無遺 (10:00)<br />\n<br />\n民陣上周三（24日）向60個駐港領事館國家（不包括朝鮮及俄羅斯）及歐盟發信，呼籲各國對港發旅遊警示，避免國民成為警察和黑勢力濫用暴力的受害者。《人民日報》海外版頭版今（29日）刊登評論文章，斥民陣的「港獨屬性暴露無遺」，意圖「裏應外合搞亂香港」。<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"49b28ac9efc98a80e4f3f4ff8c516d2ba75726c2","tid":1380584,"uid":281918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:07:46.000Z","msg":"推到泛民議員見到"},{"pid":"ed0b51d741f080fdb590c6f43885480efb2913da","tid":1380584,"uid":281918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:08:16.000Z","msg":"你哋airtime一句好重要"},{"pid":"2178078bb4fc132bb77b21ec420ddf23613794e3","tid":1380584,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T01:57:01.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f62d9c59c7a6cd3b201bff7b3346283640782e7","tid":1380584,"uid":223609,"like":0,"dis